{"tid":1777431,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"上訴庭拒頒暫緩令 警不能再執行蒙面法","createTime":"2019-12-10T08:27:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-10T10:55:42.000Z","uid":222970,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"1073212d88297b4f40018b7b77af0765bd167127","tid":1777431,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T08:27:45.000Z","msg":"上訴庭拒頒暫緩令 警不能再執行蒙面法<br />\n<br />\n政府回歸後首次動用緊急法，以此訂立蒙面法，旋即引來多宗司法覆核挑戰，高等法院早前裁定緊急法於「危害公安」可立法這部份違憲，蒙面法主要條文亦違憲。惟法院鑑於現時社會情況特殊，短期暫緩宣告違憲至今天，待政府提請上訴。政府及後向上訴庭申請暫緩執行裁決至上訴有結果，令蒙面法可繼續有效，惟上訴庭今頒下裁決，拒絕應政府申請頒下有效至上訴有結果的暫時有效令或暫緩執行令。<br />\n<br />\n換言之，原訟庭上月22日宣告緊急法和蒙面法部份條文違憲，有關宣告將會開始執行（come into operation)。<br />\n<br />\n【案件編號：HCAL2945、2949/19】<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20191210/60362840\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191210%2F60362840&d=%2BaoNGjxKkOyNIKnkVXg3ccpe%2FvQB%2B59L3xQItPRvby0%3D&h=f90d240c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191210%2F60362840&h=34fa267d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20191210/60362840</a>"},{"pid":"735522ddd70f7a6ea6608e6afc526e245d9cdada","tid":1777431,"uid":222970,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T08:28:24.000Z","msg":"我要見到全民口罩啊！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d639005429a16179d2f495861fc62795d6743130","tid":1777431,"uid":8028,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T08:29:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65621a48f0d952156dea